                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-ussec-green mb-3" data-i18n="howWeOperate.structure.headquarters.title">Global Headquarters</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="howWeOperate.structure.headquarters.description">
                  Strategic direction and coordination from our central office, ensuring alignment across all regional operations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="scroll-reveal-item" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-sec-yellow/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sec-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
